'''Riistar's Raiders''' were a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] gang affiliated with the [[Invids]]. When they were based on [[Courkrus]] in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], they tended to gather in a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] called [[The Warren]], which they shared with the ''[[Red Nova]]'' crew. Aside from the [[Khuiumin Survivors]], they fared the best during [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn's]] "Ghost [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]" operation, losing far fewer members to desertion than other Invid gangs. [[Timmser]] was a former Raider.

